                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontsize='24' underline='true'>Key Insights</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontsize='10'>-  Friday Shows the strongest projected demand and highest total artist popularity.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontsize='10'>-  Saturday underperforms despite similar lineup size and billing structure.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontsize='10'>-  Billing mix is consistent across all four days, suggesting lineup quality drives demand more than artist volume.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontsize='10'>- Lowest Top 5 artist concentration on Saturday likely explains weaker projected demand. </run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
